192
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,620
Dr. Meng said

193
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,980
Mr. Lee's condition
is temporarily under control.

194
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,740
She wants to stay
and monitor him for the night

195
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:47,860
and leave after his condition
is completely stable.

196
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:51,020
Dr. Meng is indeed thoughtful.

197
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,340
With her here,

198
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,140
I'm at ease.

199
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,020
Yes.

200
