00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,340
Thanks.

236
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,260
Why is he here?

237
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:41,340
He came to deliver
a message for Luo Han.

238
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,260
Him?

239
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,140
Yes.

240
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,620
Don't you forget

241
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:47,740
he knows everything.

242
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,740
